nt&p=847','0','agent','','0'), ('846','1','2016-06-12 22:03:28','2016-06-12 22:03:28','Born and raised in the heart of the west side, Jacob has quickly become a dominant force in the real estate world with his finger on the pulse. With impressive knowledge of Beverly Hills, Hollywood Hills and the surrounding areas, also known as the Platinum Triangle, Jacob is able to use his vast network and knowledge of the LA social scene to his advantage.\r\n\r\nA graduate of University of California, Santa Barbara, Jacob earned a degree in Communication with an emphasis in Business and Marketing. In addition, he continued his studies in Europe where focused on Architecture and urban planning. Prior to this, Jacob grew up playing on some of Los Angeles’s most competitive club soccer teams, while concurrently practicing Tae Kwon Do over the last 12 years.\r\n\r\nJacob is not new to pressure and competition. He prides himself on fighting for his clients and getting the job done with 24/7 availability, and life long hustle.\r\n\r\nWith 5 years of real estate experience under his belt, Jacob got his start working his way up from intern to agent. It was then, that he was personally mentored by The Altman Brothers, and was given invaluable hands on experience in the high-end real estate market. Now appearing as a regular on Bravo’s, Million Dollar Listing: Los Angeles, Jacob’s exposure and demand is at an all time high.','Jacob Greene','','inherit','closed','closed','','110-revision-v1','','','2016-06-12 22:03:28','2016-06-12 22:03:28','','110','http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/12/110-revision-v1/','0','revision','','0'), ('848','1','2016-06-14 22:05:17','2016-06-14 22:05:17','Athens, Ohio is home to Ohio University which is one of America’s oldest universities.  The university hosts 39,000+ students across a 1,800 acre campus and has nearly 200,000 living alumni. While Ohio University is the largest employer in the city, the local economy also greatly depends on tourism and events related to the University through local businesses.\r\n\r\nThe owner of this business created and launched an online store with the intent to connect Ohio University alumni and Athens enthusiasts with local merchandise.  Today, the website is a one stop shopping experience for customers looking for unique, authentic local made Athens products.  Starting out with just 6 local business partners and having since grown to over 40 partners, the business has expanded tremendously in a short time.  Sales for 2015 were up 300+% over 2014 and are still growing in 2016.  Sales for Jan—Mar 2016 are up 34% over the same period in 2015.\r\n\r\nThis website takes pride in products lines which celebrate and capture Athens, Ohio and the Ohio University spirit!  90% of products are drop shipped and 10% stocked inventory, with the current inventory value for items on hand at approx. $2,500.  With a small amount of physical inventory being stored/managed from a home office, the business is easily relocatable and can be operated from any location with internet access.  This business is successfully operated by one owner working full time handling all day to day operations.  As a dropship home based operation, this business has very low overhead and generates high net profit margins – 40%!\r\n\r\nGrowing since inception, this is a unique and remarkable prospect for a new owner to walk into a turnkey operation, enjoy the goodwill that has been built with established partners and capitalize on the recognition already in place to further expand its growth trend!','Dropship Ohio University And Local Area Merchandise Ecommerce Business','Athens, Ohio is home to Ohio University which is one of America’s oldest universities.  The university hosts 39,000+ students across a 1,800 acre campus and has nearly 200,000 living alumni.  While Ohio University is the largest employer in the city, the local economy also greatly depends on tourism and events related to the','publish','closed','closed','','d